bin2c - make a file or stream to be suitable for C inclusion

bin2c is program that converts input byte streams into C language char array declaration of form:

	unsigned char bin2c[] = {
		0x7f, 0x45, 0x4c, 0x46, 0x01, 0x01, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 
		0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x02, 0x00, 0x03, 0x00, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 
		0xc0, 0x83, 0x04, 0x08, 0x34, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x08, 0x08, 0x00, 0x00,
		...
	};

bin2c reads stdin when no file given.
